====================================================================================================================
Knowledge Changelog: 0.1 to 0.2
====================================================================================================================

- Changed license to MIT
- New GUI manager, with skin support (panel, mouse events, button).
- New input manager which is event oriented and have platform independent API.
- Support to infinite (up to memory) texture frames per material stage.
- Fixed crahses on deallocation of various elements.
- Fixed memory leak and bugs on md3 and md5 models.
- Fixed md5 model to prevent models using vertices with 0 weights.
- Removed physics support and demo (API was old, not maintained and not platform independent).

